{"id":199234,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/11/维权网-维权网报道引重视，安徽芜湖停止强拆（/","date":"2011-12-01T02:30:59Z","modified":"2011-12-01T02:30:59Z","title":"维权网 | 维权网报道引重视，安徽芜湖停止强拆（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"more\">      </a></span><span>（维权网信息方芳报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>日</span><span>，维权网接到安徽芜湖拆迁受害人发来的信息：“你们的报道引起当地政府重视，已经停止强拆，表示要和我们协商解决问题，谢谢你们！”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日</span><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日，本网连续报道了安徽芜湖《郑新龙电瓶上网，揭芜湖黑暗拆迁》</span><span> </span><span>《</span><span> </span><span>安徽芜湖裁定书将拆迁户安置在公厕》等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>篇反应芜湖拆迁中的严重违法问题的报道，引起了当地政府的重视，停止了强拆。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日</span><span>，芜湖市镜湖区住建委主动撤销了他们于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日</span><span>下达给郑新龙的镜房裁（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">800</span><span>号行政裁决书，并表示不会再强拆。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>近几日，其他受害人也陆续接到来自政府方面的消息，表示要和他们协商解决问题。受害人表示对当地政府知错能改感到很欣慰！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>本网将密切关注此事件的动态！</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-iPgwnE2EYdY/TtC962zXvSI/AAAAAAAADHs/bzrFLwBbRNc/s1600/%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%25A0%2587%25E9%25A2%2598-2.png\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-iPgwnE2EYdY/TtC962zXvSI/AAAAAAAADHs/bzrFLwBbRNc/s320/%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%25A0%2587%25E9%25A2%2598-2.png\" width=\"238\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" src=\"